data.name: passion
data.value: I'm a passionate software developer with a strong focus on building modern web applications, particularly using ASP.NET Razor Pages— the very framework I used for this project. This website was developed as part of my diploma thesis to showcase not just my technical abilities, but also my creativity and attention to user experience. Over the years, I've worked on several full-stack applications ranging from small business websites to internal enterprise tools. I enjoy experimenting with different web technologies and staying up-to-date with the latest trends in UI/UX design. My favorite tools and languages include C#, HTML, CSS, and frameworks like TailwindCSS for rapid and elegant UI design. I also enjoy diving into JavaScript, TypeScript, and occasionally dabbling in Python and PHP for fun or utility scripting.
